6:
Polka... Fran... Where did everybody
go?
14:
Fine. If no one's going to come
home...
15:
Then tomorrow might as well not
come either.
21: Urgh, I hate it when I fall asleep.
40:
Are you brain dead, Carla?! Slow
down, or you'll collapse again!
52: Heh... Haha... Look at how weak it is!
54: I'll punch you into next week!
60:
She'll be alright. The recovery
process has already begun, so
there's no reason to look so worried.
65:
She's just used too much power.
Every time she gets carried away,
this happens. Grinds my scales, I tell
ya.
69:
I knew she was reckless from the
moment we met her.
72:
But it's like she's trying to throw her
life away at every possible
opportunity.
76:
Believe it or not, she was worse
when we first met.
77:
I thought she was a goner for sure
back then.
80:
That's right. You guys met here in
the Kaleidoscope, didn't you?
87: She went to the depths? By herself?
92:
Damn it, I smell a shift coming! Grab
Carla, and let's scram!
103:
What are we waiting for? Move it,
people!
108: Carla! No, don't run off alone!
114:
Carla! CARLA! You idiot! Open your
eyes!
117: You guys.... Were you waiting for me?
130: Black snakes? No... It can't be...
139:
Carla, Alk and Nimbus are fighting
for you!
142:
Polka, Fran... Why did you guys leave
me?
147:
Wake up, already! This thing is not
your friend!
167:
Truth is, I'm a part of this swirling
mass. It's the part that couldn't finish
devouring your life force.
168:
So, if I give it all that juicy life I've
held up till now, maybe...
173: Cob? Don't you leave me too!
178: Don't just stare at us! Help, damn it!
188:
Tomorrow might as well not come
either.
189: So... please... don't leave me behind!
190:
The pact is sealed. We shall walk
beside you.
191: But, there will be a price.
194:
Half of our body for half of your life
force.
209: Cob, I'm sorry! I promised you...
211:
You idiot. That was your chance to
claim back your vitality.
215: Who cares. I've got you, Cob.
217:
Good enough for me. Well, we better
get Alk and Nimbus outta here, eh?
Give 'em a lift.
224:
Ahaha! All aboard the Near Death
Express!
